{"type": "article", "id": 23601, "title": "无刻度时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112454cEs5geB3pUaLzt7u.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款挂钟完全模糊了指针和刻度的概念。它由前后两个颜色不同的圆盘组成，都只带有一个很小的缺口，分别指示小时和分钟，极简但巧妙。如果不是特别注意，会忘记这是一个钟，它缓解了因时间带来的紧张感。设计者来自俄罗斯，他们设计了很多极简的时钟，这款钟有 6 种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.kibardindesign.com/products/collection/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021124521LQZEoCavew4V5P8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 211px; width: 375px; left: 628px; top: 606px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112452q0MEmrSuha63xopd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112453gfVS0u6KwpGM9ha5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021124530lNiTKEdxRJ1QYPb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}